wsintelliauction.util

Class AbstractDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • wsintelliauction.util.AbstractDriver
  • Type Parameters:
    TM - TaskManager type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Driver, Driver, Driver, Driver

    public abstract class AbstractDriver
extends java.lang.Object
    Driver superclass. All executable applications in the system must derive an implementation of this class. The driver is the entry point for any application, and is instantiated via the Main method/Main class of an application.
    Author:
    James Lewis
